  "text": "Subgroup discovery [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] differs from redescription mining in its goals. It finds queries describing groups of instances having unusual and interesting statistical properties on their target variable which are often unavailable in purely descriptive tasks. Exceptional model mining [CITATION_3] extends subgroup discovery to more complex target concepts searching for subgroups such that a model trained on this subgroup is exceptional based on some property.",
